#all(trigger[to]) chooser which holds NO targets (the event-target
#binding does not survive into/through the may-clone) -> 'if (t &&
#ability)' fails silently. AACastCard itself is correctly oneShot=false
#and would work via the addToGame branch if t were bound. Next: find
